'''''Remember Shakti – The Believer''''' is a live album by the [[world music|world fusion]] band Remember Shakti, that was released in 2000 on the [[Verve Records|Verve]] label. The live set features 
John McLaughlin on guitar, electric mandolinist [[U. Srinivas]], [[V. Selvaganesh|Vikku Selvaganesh]] playing [[ghatam]], and [[tabla]] player [[Zakir Hussain (musician)|Zakir Hussain]].The album peaked number 20 in the [[Billboard (magazine)|Billboard]] Top Jazz Albums chart.<ref name=allmusicawards>{{cite web |url= http://www.allmusic.com/album/remember-shakti-the-believer-mw0000619949/awards |title=Remember Shakti: The Believer - John McLaughlin,Shakti &#124; Awards &#124; AllMusic |work=allmusic.com |accessdate=29 April 2014}}</ref>

